#: src/brouwers/awards/templates/awards/winners.html:15
msgid ""
"The 'Brouwers Awards' can be compared to movie or music awards, but applied "
"to build report topics! Topics get nominated within a category, and everyone "
"can vote their favourites within each category, ultimately leading to a top-"
"three."
msgstr ""

#: src/brouwers/awards/templates/awards/winners.html:21
